A26: ( ( ( a * x ) - c1 ) mod m1 ) = ( 0 )
and
A27: ( ( ( b * x ) - c2 ) mod m2 ) = ( 0 );
( ( m1 div d1 ) * d1 ) divides ( ( ( ( a div d1 ) * x ) - ( c1 div d1 ) ) * d1 ) by A1,A19,A15,A16,A26,CKB55:1;
